<div class="row">
  <div class="col-12">
    <%= link_to "Back to All Demos", root_path %>
    <h1>Motion Demos - Live Preview</h1>
    <p>A pure-Ruby implementation of Live Preview, referencing an alternative approach to (<a href="https://nts.strzibny.name/rails-stimulus-live-preview/">Rails and Stimulus</a>).</p>

    <ul>
      <li>No JS is used to execute live preview, only Ruby</li>
      <li>The page is never reloaded</li>
      <li>No frontend model/store/reducer required, all state is managed in a Ruby class on the server</li>
    </ul>
  </div>


  <section class="my-4 col-sm-12 col-md-8">
    <%= render Tweets::LivePreview.new %>
  </section>
</div>
